            <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight">Secondary & Senior Secondary Education
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-white/90 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">Excellence Stage: Preparing
