                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-check text-primary-600 mt-1 mr-3"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Pick-up (Nursery-VII):</strong> Parents must receive child at bus stop
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt text-primary-600 mt-1 mr-3"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Changes:</strong> Route/stop changes require 1 month advance notice
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <i class="fas fa-envelope text-primary-600 mt-1 mr-3"></i>
                            <div>
